Titolo: CSI: Crime City

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: CSI: Crime City was the eleventh video game adaptation of the CSI: Crime Scene Investigation television series, developed for Facebook by American studio area/code and published by Ubisoft. It was the third CSI game released during 2010, along with CSI: Fatal Conspiracy and CSI: Unsolved. When Case Set 12 was released, it brought the game up to 61 cases. The game has been shut down as of March 13, 2015.